    "The receiver ID is assigned by %1$@ when it first pairs a sensor. It's saved in this app and shown on the Libre 3 settings page — write it down if you want to re-pair this sensor after reinstalling %1$@.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "comment": "Recovery screen footnote (1: appName)"
    },
